    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "OZARK\n...",
      "Serving Mid-America Best\nThe New OZARK DC-9333\nby Douglas\nThe new silhouette is no longer a shape of things to\ncome. It's here and ready to streak across the routes\nof Ozark. The DC-9, with a cruising speed of 560\nmiles per hour, shortens the total time to and from\nyour destination. Because of its rapid rate of climb,\nthe DC-9 reaches a cruising altitude in a few minutes,\naffording a smooth, relaxing ride even on short trips.\nGO-GETTERS GET UP AND GO WITH OZARK AIR LINES\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\n2015.166.1181"
    ],
